I'm Ken Tanabe. I'm from Harvard Medical School and Mass General Brigham.

8
00:00:26.060 --> 00:00:29.740
So we have a very exciting and diverse

9
00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:33.840
line of abstracts to be presented today.

10
00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:37.680
They cover a very wide range of tumor types,

11
