and they're all in this very exciting setting,

12
00:00:41.780 --> 00:00:45.540
perioperative, the neoadjuvant, and I think that presents

13
00:00:45.880 --> 00:00:49.180
very unique windows of opportunity to assess

14
00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:53.200
biomarkers and response. And so, I think it's a wonderful

15
00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:57.080
theme to chair a session on. We also have

16
00:00:57.560 --> 00:01:00.720
a very diverse and talented group of speakers, which we welcome

17
