So thank you very much.

26
00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:36.310
And with that, I'd like to welcome the very

27
00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:37.020
first speaker,

28
00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:40.560
Dr. Foote from Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center.

29
00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:48.560
We cannot see it.

30
00:01:49.020 --> 00:01:50.660
Yeah, I can't see it. I can't see the...

31
