1463
01:23:21.018 --> 01:23:24.927
First, some background. First-line treatment for early-stage HCC is surgical

1464
01:23:24.958 --> 01:23:27.278
resection and offers patients a chance for cure.

1465
01:23:27.878 --> 01:23:31.198
However, recurrence rates are significant in this cancer, with up to 80% of

1466
01:23:31.238 --> 01:23:33.658
patients recurring after surgery.

1467
01:23:34.298 --> 01:23:38.118
Currently, there are no standard or approved neoadjuvant or adjuvant systemic

1468
01:23:38.138 --> 01:23:41.828
therapies for resectable HCC, highlighting an urgent need for safe and feasible

1469
01:23:41.918 --> 01:23:43.358
systemic options in this setting.

1470
01:23:45.878 --> 01:23:49.438
Recently, there were two key negative Phase III adjuvant ICI trials in

1471
01:23:49.578 --> 01:23:52.948
HCC, including IMbrave050, the updated data, as well as

1472
01:23:52.958 --> 01:23:56.638
KEYNOTE-937. Both atezolizumab and bevacizumab, as well as

1473
01:23:56.658 --> 01:24:00.558
pembrolizumab monotherapy, did not show survival benefit over active surveillance

1474
01:24:00.618 --> 01:24:04.558
alone. This highlights the shift towards neoadjuvant and perioperative strategies.

1475
01:24:07.078 --> 01:24:10.818
Several studies recently of neoadjuvant therapies in HCC have

1476
01:24:10.858 --> 01:24:14.698
demonstrated both safety and feasibility as well as meaningful pathologic response

1477
01:24:14.758 --> 01:24:18.118
rates and tertiary lymphoid aggregate formation in

1478
01:24:19.338 --> 01:24:23.208
therapy recipients. In addition, pathologic responses have been correlated with

1479
01:24:23.238 --> 01:24:26.978
long-term survival as well. Just last year, the CARES-019

1480
01:24:27.018 --> 01:24:30.968
trial out of China was a Phase II/III trial for perioperative pembrolizumab with

1481
01:24:30.978 --> 01:24:34.518
rivicereb, a combination of PD-1 and anti-VEGF therapy

1482
01:24:34.878 --> 01:24:38.398
that showed superior event-free survival compared to active surveillance alone.

1483
01:24:38.818 --> 01:24:42.538
However, this regimen is not adopted by Western guidelines as overall

1484
01:24:42.558 --> 01:24:44.538
survival benefit has not yet been demonstrated.

1485
01:24:44.928 --> 01:24:48.858
And reflective of local HCC patterns in China, most

1486
01:24:48.898 --> 01:24:52.678
of the disease etiology in the cohort for this trial had

1487
01:24:52.798 --> 01:24:55.018
HPV-positive liver disease etiology.

1488
01:24:55.698 --> 01:24:59.598
This highlights that validation of their cohorts is necessary and additional data

1489
01:24:59.608 --> 01:25:02.078
is needed to identify the optimal perioperative regimen.

1490
01:25:03.818 --> 01:25:07.538
For the rationale for neoadjuvant nivolumab with relatimab, which is

1491
01:25:07.558 --> 01:25:11.418
anti-LAG3 monoclonal. First, fibrinogen-like 1 protein,

1492
01:25:11.498 --> 01:25:15.058
or FGL1, is a major inhibitory ligand of LAG3 and is

1493
01:25:15.098 --> 01:25:16.678
constitutively expressed in the liver.

1494
01:25:17.158 --> 01:25:20.698
An early HCC is actually enriched for adaptive immune resistance through this

1495
01:25:20.758 --> 01:25:22.458
pathway, along with the PD-1 pathway.

1496
01:25:22.858 --> 01:25:26.358
And dual PD-1 LAG3 blockade restores T cell function

1497
01:25:26.678 --> 01:25:30.518
beyond PD-1 blockade alone. And in our earlier neoadjuvant study

1498
01:25:30.598 --> 01:25:34.238
that combined nivolumab with cabozantinib, a multi-tyrosine kinase

1499
01:25:34.498 --> 01:25:38.338
inhibitor that also targets VEGF, identified higher expression of

1500
01:25:38.358 --> 01:25:41.918
LAG3 in the TILs and peripheral PBMCs of non-responders in that trial.

