01:25:42.478 --> 01:25:46.098
Also, in addition, perioperative nivolumab with

1502
01:25:46.118 --> 01:25:48.538
relatimab has shown benefit in other tumors such as melanoma.

1503
01:25:48.898 --> 01:25:50.658
However, this has not yet been studied in HCC.

1504
01:25:52.158 --> 01:25:55.998
And so here we present an open-label, non-comparative, randomized Phase II trial

1505
01:25:56.058 --> 01:25:59.638
for potentially resectable HCCFrom 2021 to '25,

1506
01:25:59.778 --> 01:26:03.578
patients were enrolled in Johns Hopkins and Ohio State's liver MDCs and were

1507
01:26:03.618 --> 01:26:07.198
