1509
01:26:11.258 --> 01:26:15.238
relatimab. Patients then underwent surgical resection, and eligible patients

1510
01:26:15.258 --> 01:26:18.018
continued to the adjuvant cycle of our trial.

1511
01:26:19.978 --> 01:26:23.218
The primary endpoint of our trial was feasibility, which was the number of patients

1512
01:26:23.278 --> 01:26:26.338
who experienced an unacceptable treatment-related adverse event that precluded

1513
01:26:26.378 --> 01:26:30.287
surgery. Secondary endpoints included proportion of complete or major pathologic

1514
01:26:30.338 --> 01:26:33.588
responses being defined as 90% or greater tumor necrosis.

1515
01:26:34.438 --> 01:26:38.108
Other secondary endpoints included objective response rate, disease-free, and

1516
01:26:38.198 --> 01:26:41.858
overall survival. And there were a couple of exploratory analyses, including LAG-3

1517
01:26:41.898 --> 01:26:45.438
receptor occupancy assays, as well as immunophenotyping of the TILs and the TME.

1518
01:26:46.028 --> 01:26:47.468
Our data cutoff was in November of last year.

1519
01:26:48.098 --> 01:26:52.078
And for table one of our trial here, we can see a diverse range of liver

1520
01:26:52.098 --> 01:26:55.727
disease etiologies, as well as a predominance of BCLC

1521
01:26:55.898 --> 01:26:59.718
stage A patients, as well as BCLC stage B and C patients were also

1522
01:26:59.758 --> 01:27:03.438
