1523
01:27:03.538 --> 01:27:07.108
HCC, including elevated AFP at baseline, large lesion diameter,

1524
01:27:07.778 --> 01:27:11.048
macrovascular invasion, and multifocal disease were also represented in this

1525
01:27:11.058 --> 01:27:11.518
cohort.

1526
01:27:13.658 --> 01:27:17.508
