1528
01:27:21.438 --> 01:27:24.658
as no patients experienced any treatment-related adverse events that precluded

1529
01:27:24.678 --> 01:27:28.648
surgery. In the nivolumab arm, three of 15 patients or 20% had

1530
01:27:28.678 --> 01:27:30.278
a complete pathologic or major

1531
01:27:31.958 --> 01:27:35.198
pathologic response. And in the combination arm, four of 15 patients or

1532
01:27:35.298 --> 01:27:39.268
26.7% had a pathologic or radiographic complete or

1533
01:27:39.358 --> 01:27:40.018
major response.

